con:request.name: Request 1
con:request.con:request:
<DatamartStoredQuery xmlns="http://openiz.org/warehousing" id="17BA63B4-50FA-41D5-9D24-7FB41606A961" name="defaulters" > <sql provider="npgsql"> <![CDATA[ WITH defaulters AS ( SELECT patient_id, MAX(-(act_date + '7 day'::INTERVAL - CURRENT_DATE)) AS days_overdue, string_agg(DISTINCT replace(mat_tbl.type_mnemonic, 'VaccineType-',''), ',') as missed_doses FROM oizcp INNER JOIN mat_tbl ON (mat_id = product_id) WHERE act_date < CURRENT_DATE - '7 DAY'::INTERVAL AND (fulfilled IS NULL OR fulfilled = FALSE) AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sbadm_tbl WHERE mat_id = product_id AND pat_id = patient_id AND seq_id = dose_seq
) GROUP BY patient_id ) SELECT defaulters.*, gender_mnemonic, dob, family, given, tel, mth_family, mth_given, mth_tel, nok_family, nok_given, nok_tel FROM defaulters INNER JOIN pat_vw ON (patient_id = pat_id) WHERE deceased IS NULL; ]]> </sql> </DatamartStoredQuery>
